        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 5. Non-metric multidimensional scaling (NMDS) plots detailing the differences between Bolitoglossa franklini, B. lincolni, B. meliana, B. qeqom, and B. tenebrosa based on morphological measurements. Measurements of the holotype (UVG- A7015), paratype (UVG-A7016), and topotypes (UTADC 9633–9640) are included in the analysis for B. qeqom. Measurements of B. tenebrosa correspond to specimen USAC 2114." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4736554/files/figure.png" .

